This is very helpful. I did find that using the example relx.config, I could never past the &quot;No goals specified for this release...&quot; error as long as the app goals list in the release tuple was empty. Modifying it like so:<p><pre><code>    {release, {erlang_app, &quot;0.1.0&quot;}, [erlang_app]}
</code></pre>
seems to do the trick.
